OL,5, Two former senior managers at a large  
OL,6, mental health care provider have told  
OL,7, the BBC they had concerns about the    
OL,8, safety of patients and staff.          
OL,10,FThe whistleblowers claim they felt     
OL,11,Fpressure to cut costs and fill beds.   
OL,13,FThe Priory Group, which receives more  
OL,14,Fthan #600m of public money each year,  
OL,15,Fis the biggest single private provider 
OL,16,Fof mental health services to the NHS.  
OL,18,FThe company denies the claims and says 
OL,19,Fit successfully treats tens of         
OL,20,Fthousands of patients each year.       
